info.name: Outlines - CSS Dev Element Tool
info.description: This Stylish will help you see where each HTML element begins and ends in the DOM.

style.css:
a						{outline:1px dotted #D68A85!important;}		/* red */
h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6	{outline:1px dotted #E7912D!important;}		/* orange */
future					{outline:1px dotted #CECC33!important;}		/* yellow */
span					{outline:1px dotted #F0F!important;}
div						{outline:1px dotted #3AB6F1!important;}		/* blue */
ul, ol					{outline:1px dotted #8684D8!important;}		/* purple */
li						{outline:1px dotted #DD67AE!important;}		/* pink */
td						{outline:1px dotted lightblue!important;}	/* lightblue */
i						{outline:1px dotted gray!important;}		/* gray */
